quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe mum mawnii, ko KaŇčko woni kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  67,2,"Oon tagir…óo maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude golle. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, kaforoowo on."
  67,3,"On tak…óo kammuuji jee…ói…ói pawondir…ói. A yi'ataa …ďura-…ďurda e tagoore jom hinaraŇčke On. Yiiltu ndaar…óe maa …óen (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ce'ekol?"
  67,4,"Refti nduttaa ndaar…óe …óen laa…ďi …ói…ói, gite maa …óeen nduttoto e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, ta∆īii…óe."
  67,5,"GooŇč…óii Min cu…óinirii kammu aduna nguun [koode] pitilli, Min mba…ói …óe fi…óir…óe seytanuuji, Min kebilani …ďe lette hu…ď…ďunge nge."
  67,6,"Hino woodani …ďeen yeddu…ďe Joomi mum, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  67,7,"Si …ďe mbeddaama e ndeer magge, …ďe nanirat nge ha'acaango, hara henge fata."
  67,8,"Henge e…ď…ďa fultagol, sabu tikkere ndeen. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaa…ďe nge …ďeen lamndoo …ďe : "E hara jeertinoowo araano e mo'on?""
  67,9,"∆Āe mbi'a: "Pellet ! Jeertinoowo arno e amen tigi, kono min njeddi min mbi'i: Allah jippinaani hay e hu'unde, on ngonaani si wonaa e ndeer majjere mawnde"."
  67,10,"∆Āe mbi'ita : "Si mi…óen nanaynoo maa hara me…óen haqqilaynoo, min njeyetanooke e yim…ďe Hu…ď…ďunge ngeen"."
  67,11,"∆Āe qirritii bakkatuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Halakuyee woodanii joom en Hu…ď…ďaynge ngen."
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ďe Joomi mum …ďeen ka wirnii, hino woodani …ďen haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi."